snippet.title: Relics of the Fallen - Trailer
snippet.description:
Now available for free on Google Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.crescentyr.relicsofthefallen

Relics of the Fallen is a dungeon crawler card game with roguelike elements.
Choose your hero and the dungeon you want to explore. Defeat monsters, collect items and relics throughout your journey.

Website: http://crescentyr.com/rotf
Twitter: https://twitter.com/crescentyr
